            "text": "The Birdsey Group, LLC, together with its affiliated companies (“Birdsey Group,” “we,” “us,” or “our”), respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect through birdseygroup.com (the “Site”), how we use and share it, and the choices available to you. By using the Site, you agree to the practices described in this Policy."
